<h2><strong>How Much Does the Boat Shipping Cost Calculator?</strong></h2>
The cost of transporting your boat may vary based on several factors, such as the size of your boat, the time of year, and other relevant considerations. For beam widths exceeding 12 feet, the estimated cost per mile ranges from $2.75 to $3.75.
<br><br>
The cost per mile decreases as the size of your boat decreases. The average price per mile to transport a boat is approximately $1.63.
